<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-3991] Exponantiation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-3991</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On command line:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;$ groovy -e &apos;println 2**63&apos; #=&amp;gt; 9223372036854775807&lt;br/&gt;
$ ruby -e &apos;puts 2**63&apos; #=&amp;gt; 9223372036854775808&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ruby is right, Groovy is wrong.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Special thanks to @datenreisender: &lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.com/datenreisender/status/6996674701&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://twitter.com/datenreisender/status/6996674701&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ruined my kata: &lt;a href=&quot;http://berndschiffer.blogspot.com/2009/12/prime-factors-kata-first-try.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://berndschiffer.blogspot.com/2009/12/prime-factors-kata-first-try.html&lt;/a&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/sad.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
